<p local-id=3D"7fc55c96-6c5f-4144-9f5a-c7a5ae278a25"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"6bfccbdf-c31f-4ce7-bbc2-9b238b549aae" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-UserGuide"><strong>User Guide</strong></h1>
<p local-id=3D"ea24316b-e374-427d-8029-4f3605628a0d">Complete step-by-step =
guide to using <strong>Labamu Manufacturing (MRP)</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c38624ba-040c-4f93-bef5-463313b835fe">This guide walks you t=
hrough the entire manufacturing workflow, from setup to production tracking=
. You can plan, produce, and monitor efficiently.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"bef45bb3-ff36-44c2-878f-32ae2d271e5c">
<h3 local-id=3D"b4401aca-5aa1-4e7a-b79c-65df188ddcc8" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step1:GettingStarted"><strong>Step 1: Getting Started</strong=
></h3>
<p local-id=3D"851f568e-07dd-4fbe-8e35-e2b8c2cbd9b9">Set up your account an=
d understand the basics.</p>
<p local-id=3D"81c8b50d-e574-4c7e-ae85-8b00e69e4c67"><strong>What you need =
to know:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"903b22d2-c863-4d30-807b-1ea78f07a7fc">
<li local-id=3D"0d3e3680-1a68-418b-83c5-82149ae3058f">
<p local-id=3D"675ac304-417f-4d07-a1ab-05e9e98c3848">MRP is automatically a=
vailable once your business is activated for the Manufacturing app on Labam=
u.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1a9877b-8799-42db-a0fe-4fd803995386">
<p local-id=3D"0d8aa0b0-6e94-47e3-b715-c9497c212ae4">It connects directly w=
ith <strong>Products</strong>, <strong>Materials</strong>, <strong>BOM (Bil=
l of Materials)</strong>, and <strong>Routing</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a2a9806f-2c2a-4862-9489-d77a8c5aa764">
<p local-id=3D"71172865-82df-4078-aa88-a86f20668b77">Each production order =
follows this flow:<br><strong>Material Planning =E2=86=92 RFQ =E2=86=92 Quo=
tes =E2=86=92 Order =E2=86=92 Work Order =E2=86=92 Production Tracking =E2=
=86=92 Completion</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3462296-9a94-4d4b-a8ce-25732cd48f67">
<p local-id=3D"e3304a18-e203-4c4d-90de-dbb786666767">Ensure your master dat=
a (Products, Materials, BOM, and Routing) is uploaded before creating an Or=
der.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"dd371022-9db5-4793-861b-b152248da021">
<h3 local-id=3D"5ae94409-f2a4-4109-986d-72860a3be551" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step2:ManageMaterials"><strong>Step 2: Manage Materials</stro=
ng></h3>
<p local-id=3D"813dcfd4-e048-4752-87ea-69fa01c09b9a">Define all raw materia=
ls or components used in your production.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"16b7fe21-8b96-42cf-acc7-7122a7370304" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateMaterials:"><strong>How to Create Materials:</stro=
ng></h3><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrappe=
r confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image =
image-center" alt=3D"image-20251010-063335.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"la=
zy" src=3D"14eb23eaf2e338d43064616aa952eb2668243490cd6585139d7ab59a516e3a84=
" data-image-src=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attac=
hments/1464336406/image-20251010-063335.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDat=
e=3D1760078019490&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"916" da=
ta-width=3D"2668" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-=
id=3D"1472036868" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-t=
ype=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-063=
335.png" data-base-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-li=
nked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=
=3D"1464336406" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=
=3D"5130b833-db47-41f3-8754-0398b68900f1" data-media-type=3D"file" height=
=3D"160"></span>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"aef78613-1477-4fa0-b56c-5f3e5078272e">
<li local-id=3D"04965685-76b4-4a74-a4bb-02595c21ba85">
<p local-id=3D"eabb21dc-5487-4341-bb6e-7b13c389883b">Navigate to <strong>Ma=
nufacturing =E2=86=92 Materials</strong> in the sidebar.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d15d7f14-5932-45a9-8977-da892a73f133">
<p local-id=3D"499440e5-a9fe-48c8-a4e1-d313cdef22a2">Click <strong>New Mate=
rial</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4abff888-5ab4-4aad-bcef-f637bc2fd094">
<p local-id=3D"ec2c659d-78d1-43a3-8ea4-ad89937339ff">Fill in the details as=
 shown below:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"90578cdc-bee6-47d0-a0b5-04d9f08411e7">
<li local-id=3D"4bdd93ee-11eb-4732-9d9a-a5bc958c3114">
<p local-id=3D"ff43759e-a9e9-499e-92c7-87948481bc46"><strong>SKU</strong> =
=E2=80=93 Auto-generated if left empty.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71b158ef-874c-4bc4-8b09-18748aefcca8">
<p local-id=3D"8cda5aa1-b1d9-4390-a48d-c46a06a9dae1"><strong>Material Name<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the material name (e.g., <em>Steel Pla=
te 2mm</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b563dd06-717e-4383-87f9-d40231afb506">
<p local-id=3D"37fb3b9b-6c18-4ec0-9853-e7ea886a3b85"><strong>Category</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Select or create a material category (e.g., <em>M=
etal</em>, <em>Plastic</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0b8f484-2b82-4dab-9edb-ab22c98ce084">
<p local-id=3D"827970c8-fb84-4a2e-b5fc-b31ffb9c82eb"><strong>ABC Classifica=
tion</strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Choose classification based on value or=
 importance (A =3D High Value, B =3D Medium, C =3D Low).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c0f488d-85a6-4d8a-8cc6-5d3d71c73cd9">
<p local-id=3D"ac554eb1-157f-40c0-8e2a-1b346b097e15"><strong>Material Type<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Choose <em>Raw Material</em>, <em>Sub Materi=
al</em>, or <em>Consumable</em>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae39676f-1748-462e-a520-8366b88e8521">
<p local-id=3D"5b50e31b-8151-4202-ab66-26f8500e37d7"><strong>Unit of Measur=
e</strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Select or create the measurement unit (e.g=
., <em>pcs</em>, <em>kg</em>, <em>mL</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9bd9d6bc-b9f1-43ad-8b63-3ba8d26b1df8">
<p local-id=3D"ad5a1f3d-7854-42ce-9dc4-45bcd5b6a428"><strong>Description</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Add a short note about the material.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33d26cc0-c5c8-4d84-8808-ae4ad2f0f21d">
<p local-id=3D"f0a42171-8133-4ae8-8c71-04a465073f3c"><strong>Is Stockable</=
strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Keep this checked if the material should be tr=
acked in inventory.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"672cfecd-ab87-4165-8c1d-057855e37446">
<p local-id=3D"c338d991-df1d-4786-85fd-e99c32ef2e81"><strong>Image</strong>=
 =E2=80=93 (Optional) Upload an image to help visually identify the materia=
l.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"672cfecd-ab87-4165-8c1d-057855e37446">
<p local-id=3D"c338d991-df1d-4786-85fd-e99c32ef2e81">Click <strong>Save</st=
rong> at the top right corner.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"b37722fb-7003-4370-ac9c-6936251be1ce"><strong>Tips:</strong>=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"96e7b7f9-7389-4696-b01c-82e8b14eba22">
<li local-id=3D"e7cd9595-1f2c-4715-a970-d31f213fbe6b">
<p local-id=3D"3ad9c34c-9ded-404a-83c7-5e7fa8f77864"><strong>SKU</strong> w=
ill be automatically generated if left blank.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4a602095-8fef-4716-8cbc-58b9e4c5f119">
<p local-id=3D"e42d7b8c-dc33-4ac1-b6b6-7bf2891cb5c8">You can use <strong>Bu=
lk Upload</strong> to import multiple materials via Excel template.</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"974e63e0-3c0a-4250-8412-00866fdf203c">
<p local-id=3D"81767b50-4de4-4152-8919-ac414e433c35">Only <strong>Active</s=
trong> materials can be used in <strong>BOM</strong> (Bill of Materials) an=
d <strong>Work Orders</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c85a4cd-dac9-4b16-9eb8-64de078e9210">
<p local-id=3D"956e2d06-e5fd-47d2-bf25-1ccc3dde6062">Maintain consistent na=
ming conventions for easier tracking and reporting.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d71bd9d8-5b60-424e-9a1a-c37dc13a2285" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateBatches:">How to Create Batches:</h3><span class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedd=
ed-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=
=3D"image-20251010-063616.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c88ebf=
ac5a7cd07b03afb85a7db037fa63413674bcfd30e7c244fe464447999f" data-image-src=
=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/146433640=
6/image-20251010-063616.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D176007818028=
5&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"428" data-width=3D"2612=
" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1472659459=
" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachmen=
t" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-063616.png" data-ba=
se-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-co=
ntent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1464336406" d=
ata-linked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"84fcdb73-1101=
-446d-a6cf-88a3cb5970fa" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"76"></span>
<p local-id=3D"b0cfa7e9-7919-4623-b1bf-ed23c58bb043">Each material can have=
 multiple <strong>batches</strong> to track stock quantity, expiry, and ven=
dor details. This helps you manage materials more accurately.</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"824ed100-d519-4d9c-8045-9979cdd05780">
<li local-id=3D"1b1e53fc-f8f0-453f-9b20-7ae444984267">
<p local-id=3D"1245a590-7ce9-434f-a9c1-277347228b93">Open the <strong>mater=
ial</strong> you want to manage (for example, <em>Table</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"658e3629-638f-48ff-961d-23be48fb9b9c">
<p local-id=3D"e0392d31-4d1d-4244-9f3e-314d2fc6b258">Go to the <strong>Stoc=
k Batches</strong> tab.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be3efea1-a611-42d1-87c6-e258ccdaa780">
<p local-id=3D"9872d799-60db-4bd4-82e2-486e6fbee1f4">Click <strong>+ New Ba=
tch</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a9b89b1-20af-4be8-8c04-7369401a277e">
<p local-id=3D"f18829fb-d231-4243-9362-8326038bac4f">Fill in the following =
details:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0a4d3006-bd9f-4b7f-aa97-f04890d2c6ce">
<li local-id=3D"d81fc4b0-d15e-4646-844f-74b3e9fe6397">
<p local-id=3D"734f81ae-50e8-416b-ac38-75e2a64f5c13"><strong>Initial Quanti=
ty</strong> =E2=80=94 (Mandatory) Enter the total quantity received or prod=
uced (e.g., <em>100</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2e3fe96-eebd-4830-b349-ce14a183811c">
<p local-id=3D"94993604-e05f-43b4-b726-6a360fee6b8f"><strong>Cost per Unit<=
/strong> =E2=80=94 (Optional) Input the cost of the material per unit. (e.g=
., <em>100.000</em>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e14cc62-66c7-4547-86db-2b514a961b18">
<p local-id=3D"5ef5e1d2-8670-40a2-a061-7a768195bd47"><strong>Purchase Date<=
/strong> =E2=80=94 (Mandatory) Select the date when the material was receiv=
ed or purchased.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfb0e960-97d5-418d-9b33-89ee5fbe8e42">
<p local-id=3D"facec36b-0020-480c-8046-3641948286ff"><strong>Expiry Date</s=
trong> =E2=80=94 (Optional) Add an expiry or best-before date if applicable=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16f96a9c-bad6-41a4-8408-725e3a265797">
<p local-id=3D"38433ccd-7582-4b23-bec2-3feeabcc98b6"><strong>Status</strong=
> =E2=80=94 (Mandatory) Choose one of the following:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"61a55632-6aea-4435-94f7-cdc2a904f71b">
<li local-id=3D"ad4c4cee-a179-4279-8e6b-2e5edc1d98ce">
<p local-id=3D"346a5d1e-3a97-444a-8daf-df85c635a319"><em>Requested</em> =E2=
=80=93 Batch requested but not yet received.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c10fb6be-ea99-4e39-ae7a-ada2937ad029">
<p local-id=3D"ae578eb1-32e2-4ee5-88f4-e43ca0ad5244"><em>Expected</em> =E2=
=80=93 Batch is expected to arrive.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f35f8b28-be29-4b5d-9739-a8e592c63c11">
<p local-id=3D"49786217-73e2-4871-bcd0-01ff38449d58"><em>Delayed</em> =E2=
=80=93 Delivery delayed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f45b81b-99d8-4a50-8544-d183fb469d16">
<p local-id=3D"705e22da-6fb1-4c49-8f4f-ccce564691f4"><em>Received</em> =E2=
=80=93 Material has been received and available in stock.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"80e44f3b-785d-44a5-9577-b90ae478a9ec">
<p local-id=3D"73f42f8f-bba1-4868-a29a-5566ed475f0a"><strong>Storage Locati=
on</strong> =E2=80=94 (Optional) Enter where the batch is stored (e.g., <em=
>Warehouse A, Rack 3B</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ceff8a3e-0cae-4812-a92a-ce00f7b05923">
<p local-id=3D"f92be8bd-246e-49de-819e-bd4e1699fe9a"><strong>Vendor</strong=
> =E2=80=94 (Optional) Select the vendor if applicable.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc5713aa-f63d-4671-8ba2-ecd5cbcbaf5c">
<p local-id=3D"9d120d07-dcb5-49a2-9c84-ae683d65a903">After filling all fiel=
ds, click <strong>Save Batch</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"897f2ecf-0f32-4cd0-be68-43b092054a97">
<p local-id=3D"0aa32d39-100d-479a-96c0-c7cef2884c74">To add another batch, =
click <strong>+ New Batch</strong> again.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"981d65bf-50b5-4228-bde5-4beea4315ee4" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Notes:">Notes:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0bb5bc9d-1a7e-4b30-871c-1823ff5b75aa">
<li local-id=3D"d280bbc5-d475-479d-b7d6-122673ecbb2f">
<p local-id=3D"75ed1a9d-4ed8-4545-a480-254f2380b9ac">The system automatical=
ly generates a <strong>Batch ID</strong> =E2=80=94 no need to fill it manua=
lly.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52a029d0-8576-47d6-9fdf-f582b9c796ab">
<p local-id=3D"ea074ab0-90ac-42ec-a1bc-ee89faece930"><strong>Current Quanti=
ty </strong>will follow the <strong>Initial Quantity</strong> entered durin=
g the first creation of the batch.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"90e63c3b-6509-414f-957c-0705f9f76982">
<p local-id=3D"d75739b7-1829-48e1-ba71-c8f6eea407b1">You can filter batches=
 by <strong>Status</strong>, <strong>Vendor</strong>, or <strong>Expiry</st=
rong> using the search options below the batch list.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4a68d8f-8fdc-4143-bbe1-b2732881a73d">
<p local-id=3D"7a8c502d-2808-4538-88f9-4eec2fd789d2">Use <strong>Show Empty=
 Batches</strong> to display all inactive or depleted batches.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dbc4e4b4-c0ad-4720-be45-3924bc46c15c">
<p local-id=3D"78bf8ef8-2b64-44f4-9bff-fac7a53eff29">Always ensure <strong>=
purchase and expiry dates</strong> are valid to avoid errors.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"bd46c2bf-c388-4a03-a8ac-32ac6774733e">
<h3 local-id=3D"a4c03b74-9a68-4610-be7e-60d359abf2bd" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step3:CreateRouting"><strong>Step 3: Create Routing</strong><=
/h3>
<p local-id=3D"190007da-18e9-40d7-a2ad-c5b2072a8cf5">Define the sequence of=
 stages required to manufacture a product. Each routing stage represents a =
specific operation in your production process.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"7082a547-d405-46e2-9475-4ae5eacff02f" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateRouting">How to Create Routing</h3><span class=3D"=
confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-m=
anual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"im=
age-20251010-063900.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"98e5dfe86645=
93f6c153951f1dc637e76e96e152d7f0dd82d440b5553767d528" data-image-src=3D"htt=
ps://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1464336406/image=
-20251010-063900.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1760078344309&amp;c=
acheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1084" data-width=3D"2548" data=
-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1471250438" data=
-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" dat=
a-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-063900.png" data-base-url=
=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-=
type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1464336406" data-li=
nked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"1b33831f-0b23-4624-=
9124-10ced8c146bc" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"198"></span>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"0e7d73a5-4d9c-45ee-b1ce-74ff0b45ad55">
<li local-id=3D"773a0b05-f2cb-4ca6-bd99-d7a200c5c6b9">
<p local-id=3D"f7664c42-277c-4118-abb3-309f693dc615">Navigate to Manufactur=
ing =E2=86=92 Routing in the sidebar.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80885ae4-77fe-4646-944d-28d6d8704f45">
<p local-id=3D"d61d28fa-c777-405e-96eb-0d17fd958f93">Click Add Stage on the=
 top right corner.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d7bebf0-ad42-4705-8766-613022ee0724">
<p local-id=3D"027bc6cc-041b-4088-ad86-caa4b0715a07">Fill in the following =
details in the popup form:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"efd57583-03fb-433b-9565-302560483ed7">
<li local-id=3D"de20cf7b-9e38-41c1-b4eb-bfd6b06c960b">
<p local-id=3D"acb8aea2-2b09-4d21-9b33-e9187a0409ca">Routing Name =E2=80=93=
 (Mandatory) Enter the stage name (e.g., Cutting, Assembly, Quality Assuran=
ce).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81114bba-4efd-466a-a1bf-06c671298b2f">
<p local-id=3D"90eb4561-962e-41ff-99b5-1f0e4bb21158">Routing Description =
=E2=80=93 (Optional) Add details about the operation or purpose of this sta=
ge.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b6ab30b-46e9-4828-aa7d-9871dde33255">
<p local-id=3D"c5e8f31d-1cc6-439a-bb13-f9f6003de752">Click Save to create t=
he routing stage.</p></li>
</ol>
<h4 local-id=3D"2410b4e1-ff74-4e85-9b0b-7976ba7fcd36" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Notes:.1">Notes:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"776a08f4-2ab1-47c5-b779-b3ecbd867218">
<li local-id=3D"b68cd056-3ebd-468a-9979-02c29720c319">
<p local-id=3D"bb29a3c7-9d01-4402-8d60-652ab7936060">You can create multipl=
e routing stages to define your full production workflow.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e755c6bf-34b2-43fb-b983-3d86df91097c">
<p local-id=3D"ffefb126-29d4-4c16-b190-3649f9348016">Keep stage names clear=
 and consistent (e.g., Cutting =E2=86=92 Welding =E2=86=92 Painting =E2=86=
=92 Quality Check).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eece9b8c-7ff8-41c2-8d9e-d37c77a16e90">
<p local-id=3D"a67b6846-68ab-487f-a374-3d4686fbf0a2">Routing stages will be=
 used later in Work Orders to define the manufacturing sequence and progres=
s tracking.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1041c598-3c43-4d20-ada7-d36fb783abe0">
<h3 local-id=3D"e4823a0f-1e3a-4c9a-851e-bfdc15806a12" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step4:CreateBillofMaterials(BOM)"><strong>Step 4: Create Bill=
 of Materials (BOM)</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"cde5c09c-2ba7-48af-94c9-3c664d26b0b8">Define the list of mat=
erials and production stages required to manufacture a product. The Bill of=
 Materials (BOM) connects materials, quantities, and routing steps into a c=
omplete production recipe.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"a2bcd255-b3a1-44b3-9bb6-7139c2025d41" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateaBOM">How to Create a BOM</h3><span class=3D"confl=
uence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual=
-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-2=
0251013-060439.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"618f0854282ac16a4=
7a9c93230d903469a657043309b93a9099a3b2878b1afb0" data-image-src=3D"https://=
scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1464336406/image-2025=
1013-060439.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1760335483771&amp;cacheV=
ersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"729" data-width=3D"1730" data-unres=
olved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1478098969" data-linke=
d-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-link=
ed-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251013-060439.png" data-base-url=3D"ht=
tps://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=
=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1464336406" data-linked=
-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"e0ec7b4a-f0fb-40cf-892c=
-6134c73d2eb3" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"197"></span>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"fb21beb4-9477-404b-af6d-22943ab0a0ed">
<li local-id=3D"ea7a808e-1c1c-46e1-af5c-8d7fdacefc23">
<p local-id=3D"02fce1a9-786d-44e9-a8bf-94dacfdb9ead">Navigate to Manufactur=
ing =E2=86=92 Bill of Materials in the sidebar.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1cecdadd-284e-4370-9d5a-a4f0d0071d3a">
<p local-id=3D"da5127e7-4551-4226-b444-e28a14bd0e4f">Click New BOM at the t=
op right corner.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de5bf837-2097-469c-b926-9458c47f3f49">
<p local-id=3D"539ba3db-613d-4fa5-889b-316e0122cbae"><span class=3D"inline-=
comment-marker" data-ref=3D"39699a67-df5a-4b03-a0c7-3b75d00eed82">Fill in t=
he Recipe Information:</span></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3734c9f9-fd8a-4599-b033-69bc50de59c2">
<li local-id=3D"01228c29-bf3c-45d6-b5d4-ffea00689816">
<p local-id=3D"caf20162-bdb7-4b4d-91cf-d4d4757da021">Recipe Name =E2=80=93 =
(Mandatory) Enter a unique name for this recipe (e.g., <em>Recipe A</em>).<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d883228c-e2aa-4f62-87f3-8e95f14f1e50">
<p local-id=3D"e4aad4c3-6124-4f16-a69a-9101666a9127">Description =E2=80=93 =
(Optional) Add notes about the purpose or version of the BOM.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e87d95c-0da8-43cf-b46a-742c84beb39f">
<p local-id=3D"01f70b44-04f1-419b-bc8f-21b3f9bc2ac4">Add Materials:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6436f9c3-5e1c-474b-a996-67cec91a5b7e">
<li local-id=3D"1d17e4e9-5d23-40c9-8a64-44c31a91d8fa">
<p local-id=3D"e4238c7e-214f-4ede-9725-709ae061a42d">Click Add Material.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"774f159e-74b8-430c-a748-35255ec547d5">
<p local-id=3D"333b181c-6a7a-4b75-bbca-2cf74ab53bdf">Select a Material from=
 the dropdown (Mandatory).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2115b934-d2ca-48b5-8877-46f3267f3b81">
<p local-id=3D"95714a05-cd92-4bdc-881a-b15089772c00">Enter the Quantity req=
uired per unit of product (Mandatory) (e.g., <em>2</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ee4e8a9-0be3-4d6f-8a74-f813a1cdc757">
<p local-id=3D"1cd5c3f7-239c-4a3d-8acf-e08aff927d46">Click Add Material to =
confirm.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cbbd2b5-e1b7-4e71-ae98-b0f487c41f16">
<p local-id=3D"26648f84-7fc2-4715-90c2-37b0c762fd34">Add Routing Stages (op=
tional):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bb97d6d1-e3bc-4a45-9638-faad32079242">
<li local-id=3D"8ca1b753-2882-4821-86b3-59e05a79eee1">
<p local-id=3D"9cc0427f-0ab5-4bea-84f7-e1161b8793f3">Click Add Routing Stag=
e.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d6da6a95-a015-4d36-b27d-579c70af7717">
<p local-id=3D"b08275ef-30e8-4922-8b9a-e26f27f2097d">Select a Stage Name (M=
andatory) (e.g., <em>Cutting Raw Material</em>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce02a09a-b273-4fe7-9c42-8ee921626a83">
<p local-id=3D"f6c1c4f2-e3dd-46eb-b464-aec98697555e">Choose the Routing wor=
kflow.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c5b44f2-44c6-411b-8563-037d8576f296">
<p local-id=3D"223b80fe-3a5e-4551-b431-a07a06516e1b">Enter the Step Number =
(sequence order) and estimated Hours (Mandatory) (e.g., <em>2 hours</em>).<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac0622cd-5532-4f12-8898-9771cae57015">
<p local-id=3D"fca39a47-041c-4065-bd1a-bad69a785f47">Click Add Routing Stag=
e to confirm.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"dd9bb7a1-c8da-4490-99b3-a9f6e12f1c97">
<p local-id=3D"03107ab9-02ae-4926-b53b-4dc56f6c1857">Add Forecasted Cost of=
 Goods Sold:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5a45b6b8-5654-406b-854e-eaa2339c7ded">
<li local-id=3D"200ee0e6-0705-4962-9a32-9182b9605db0">
<p local-id=3D"e838868b-d99d-4700-9a98-134d90728b90"><strong>Material Cost<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 Automatically calculated based on the average material p=
rice available.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80e65c55-f3d4-4ddc-9ece-fa9ea1bf3aca">
<p local-id=3D"942f2529-dbd6-4907-9109-45ea73a75d4c"><strong>Labour Cost</s=
trong> <em>(Optional)</em> =E2=80=93 Cost of labor required to produce one =
unit.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"024fa95c-27d1-447b-a44d-1e27b08a716d">
<p local-id=3D"558f9662-f630-45f5-ab97-165bf67c3d09"><strong>Packing Cost</=
strong> <em>(Optional)</em> =E2=80=93 Cost of packaging the product.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"024fa95c-27d1-447b-a44d-1e27b08a716d">
<p local-id=3D"558f9662-f630-45f5-ab97-165bf67c3d09"><strong>Other Cost</st=
rong> <em>(Optional)</em> =E2=80=93 Any additional costs.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"31d5a086-7800-425f-bc71-eb6103b6faef">
<p local-id=3D"fd57669d-2346-47cc-a451-4ab49e5977d7">When all details are c=
omplete, click Save at the top right corner.</p></li>
</ol>
<h4 local-id=3D"6d1341b4-6d87-4118-999e-381b2921c27c" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Notes:.2">Notes:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"e066681d-b489-4510-84dd-f3c987c1c1c5">
<li local-id=3D"f437e77a-6738-4078-8b3f-e640c5da0c3b">
<p local-id=3D"3a8b7f4a-a30a-40d4-8b7b-298ea605fa17">You can mark a BOM as =
Active or Non-Active.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a85f075b-e634-4de0-8c1f-d6bc1b759cc9">
<p local-id=3D"35c633e1-d521-4b44-b1aa-38dbb40096f1">Changing a BOM to Non-=
Active will automatically unlink it from all associated products.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe452d64-cd45-498a-a462-fe3673dfbd08">
<p local-id=3D"5db47d0a-65ed-4e1c-8ec8-95f0d077c7ad">Only Active BOMs can b=
e used in Work Orders and Production Scheduling.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3670447f-63a1-47b0-95f1-f4c3752d1746">
<p local-id=3D"3f71c5a7-4f05-4462-ae48-2d2b712668dc">The <strong>total Fore=
casted Cost of Goods Sold</strong> will be used as the <strong>Base Price</=
strong> of the product when selecting a BOM in the product setup.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a31b82a0-15b5-4ed3-a6d9-4d6fcf5dc7e3">
<h3 local-id=3D"ce4cc5f1-0ed4-4379-9404-8701fae6a769" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step5:CreateProducts"><strong>S</strong>tep 5: Create Product=
s</h3>
<p local-id=3D"271776f6-8ebd-4f75-8844-772655f8c106">Define finished goods =
or semi-finished products that will be produced using materials and routing=
. Each product serves as the final output of your Bill of Materials (BOM).<=
/p>
<h3 local-id=3D"b54ad2ad-5340-486f-8c0b-1586697a1497" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateaProduct">How to Create a Product</h3><span class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedd=
ed-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=
=3D"image-20251010-064411.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"733678=
7f545e568a6ce3c6e6411db59422fed28e7c17d3de2141ef67176fd2bd" data-image-src=
=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/146433640=
6/image-20251010-064411.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D176007865524=
8&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1208" data-width=3D"275=
0" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"147177472=
7" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachme=
nt" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-064411.png" data-b=
ase-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-c=
ontent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1464336406" =
data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"a9ad8d23-f7d=
1-4b78-8c76-7cbe5b3236d2" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"205"></span>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"209db199-1498-43e7-a107-0b126e64649b">
<li local-id=3D"691c68e9-b94d-49db-9b4b-3eddd457135b">
<p local-id=3D"602ea6d2-b7f0-407f-9cd8-060d93b78457">Navigate to Products =
=E2=86=92 Product in the sidebar.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"acc2bd32-60b6-477f-8b1a-348fa310d6b0">
<p local-id=3D"b3e5f7ab-1b6d-464a-9731-8a73a55395d7">Click New Product at t=
he top right corner.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4e74554-0cf8-4172-931a-e665ceb7bda4">
<p local-id=3D"e7b869de-0e70-4b19-be7c-e5791b9a4de8">Fill in the Basic Info=
rmation section:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7e522706-09b2-4c6a-877f-9188c0489418">
<li local-id=3D"c6a37a3f-e0ec-47ad-9434-11cdde87575e">
<p local-id=3D"772cc19a-3b74-4253-b65c-af7cc3c80e60">Product Name =E2=80=93=
 (Mandatory) Enter the product name (e.g., Stainless Steel Table).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d51c075e-b558-4a17-9c08-9c80d84b7a2e">
<p local-id=3D"0a76c914-6f2d-4b37-be2b-8c4d3ab4f4a7">SKU =E2=80=93 (Optiona=
l) Automatically generated if left empty (e.g., TBL-002).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e213fe2-401e-4355-975b-305a194f5c12">
<p local-id=3D"4dbd7924-bd65-4e8e-8e66-c1448772ae81">Category =E2=80=93 (Ma=
ndatory) Select or create a product category (e.g., Furniture, Electronics)=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58804d10-b220-4f37-a34e-9237969d65b0">
<p local-id=3D"1f30267a-e1ac-4c07-a812-eb38fbd29b61">Status =E2=80=93 (Mand=
atory) Choose Active if the product should be available for use (e.g., Acti=
ve).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c4ced01-43d5-473c-b94d-25b9e808faa1">
<p local-id=3D"85b313f9-8bc8-4072-a78d-5713bd6bea3e">Description =E2=80=93 =
(Optional) Add additional details about the product.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"7b9242cd-9ebf-40d0-953e-5abf4b0a7f27">
<p local-id=3D"ede67041-8092-4b71-8b57-e6fb07564c8c">(Optional) Upload Prod=
uct Images:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cb154651-1c00-4662-af5f-b74dc702247e">
<li local-id=3D"4df68482-a9dc-4952-8f02-a9c5158ba1f1">
<p local-id=3D"e4361dda-1b45-4f4f-967d-710c471ad4c6">Click Select Images or=
 drag and drop image files.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f2578d5-d0f4-425e-b082-54bc2e4e1a9a">
<p local-id=3D"34c085bc-bebc-428b-a27b-6090303fe755">The first uploaded ima=
ge will be set as the primary display image.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"940b45f8-68aa-4ce3-89ea-f59a717ae235">
<p local-id=3D"8671d0d5-84c4-48f8-8f15-4323eeef409e">In the Pricing &amp; L=
ogistics section:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b10ad192-c6f1-4504-956a-9986d0cf1ffd">
<li local-id=3D"5bff529f-090a-4627-83c5-7adec112daaa">
<p local-id=3D"7db26956-02f9-467c-9e79-0f5e21f76f3e">Bill of Materials =E2=
=80=93 (Optional) Select the BOM that defines how this product is made.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"8a6a259f-020d-4eed-8255-6593d07709ec">
<p local-id=3D"51acad6d-48b8-48ba-acf3-a382f9f9a578">Base Price =E2=80=93 (=
Mandatory) Input the cost per unit (e.g., IDR 100.000).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c358109-e935-409b-ae15-77f98dad4f83">
<p local-id=3D"dd6c08b0-5bc5-4384-a30c-0ab3f0bb0e6b">Selling Price =E2=80=
=93 (Mandatory) Enter the final price that will appear in sales modules (e.=
g., IDR 200.000).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5cd8a98d-da11-4590-a09a-142576cb861f">
<p local-id=3D"19577077-1ed3-412a-8553-3239825e5c1c">Lead Time =E2=80=93 (M=
andatory) Define the estimated production time (e.g., 2 weeks).</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d3f2bdc-78f0-4bd1-b86f-a86665124b1d">
<p local-id=3D"4f65e41b-ea92-488c-a9bd-2f69116da98a">Click Save at the top =
right corner to create the product.</p></li>
</ol>
<h4 local-id=3D"3ed75a4e-bc97-4d9d-8b35-0a17ce9401b3" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Notes:.3">Notes:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"0560782e-c703-4c93-84ad-841bcc2eefd5">
<li local-id=3D"9d7bc9b2-c67d-434c-9820-6e3a8736a167">
<p local-id=3D"46f04d9a-b64e-493a-9a2d-185746cea9e2">Products can be linked=
 directly to a BOM and Routing to define how they=E2=80=99re produced.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"60587312-287d-4de3-bfb0-c3e5d314258a">
<p local-id=3D"ffbaf842-8dda-470c-a752-ecc039a715b9">Keep product names cle=
ar and consistent with BOM naming conventions.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b9b2d85-325d-4dc6-835b-ec42ae2cf661">
<p local-id=3D"81d9c60d-1590-42cc-bd62-6529bdba1624">You can edit or deacti=
vate products anytime from the product list.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b27cad15-b800-4827-911c-555c2d0df22a">
<p local-id=3D"49c71e1b-bbca-4455-9723-39a95e9c9346">Uploading product imag=
es helps for catalog or sales purposes.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a30b195d-cae8-4675-8e4c-ea0a67543a06">
<p local-id=3D"fa1600e1-4959-4970-80c9-2efb507e5fa0">Product that created w=
ithout BOM cannot be use for Creating RFQ, Quote, Order</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc793c65-3398-46d3-87c7-3846723953e3">
<p local-id=3D"09e68ae3-20ac-4019-9cf6-404628a32029">Product Inactive canno=
t be use for Creating RFQ, Quote, Order</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3475e78f-8977-4a52-892a-bc7be6511c08">
<h3 local-id=3D"c196f439-b219-408a-9b90-d64d325e6274" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step6:RequestforQuotation(RFQ)"><strong>Step 6: Request for Q=
uotation (RFQ)</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"4483dc0b-0532-4543-9d33-33bc22dcef20">Plan and manage your m=
aterial procurement process by sending RFQs (Requests for Quotation) to sup=
pliers based on your production needs.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"36737293-0868-4d47-96c3-bfdab3484de6" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateanRFQ"><strong>How to Create an RFQ</strong></h3><=
span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper conflue=
nce-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-cen=
ter" alt=3D"image-20251010-064813.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=
=3D"653173214800bcf1e1495800c7ca9442e55b524d7d6d067c8bb2171f13275849" data-=
image-src=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/=
1464336406/image-20251010-064813.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D176=
0078896568&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1538" data-wid=
th=3D"2754" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"=
1471283207" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D=
"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-064813.pn=
g" data-base-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-r=
esource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"146=
4336406" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"fb7=
6b709-3f20-4331-b91e-d8aff44685c6" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"261">=
</span>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f8a8a942-93c9-4602-9195-7ed8ab2cd48e">
<li local-id=3D"90aa5f82-ffcf-4c03-bb8b-8f1eb92b8283">
<p local-id=3D"404aac6f-1943-4201-8174-9684a22744da">Navigate to <strong>Pr=
ocurement =E2=86=92 RFQ</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6f5c673-384c-4b22-89d2-3efd410da88d">
<p local-id=3D"0bea9ca2-099c-44da-8b79-777baee24cb4">Click <strong>New RFQ<=
/strong> to open the creation form.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"20318597-68f4-4c1f-9064-d0151cff8555">
<p local-id=3D"384f9d8a-5eab-4c26-b62d-d9eb90ff93cf">Fill in the <strong>Cu=
stomer Information</strong> section:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e1356635-06ae-4182-adda-85c9ade0f429">
<li local-id=3D"d380559b-6408-484f-9aad-fe48169c4e66">
<p local-id=3D"8a653ebc-93be-4a4b-9be8-a523d0649156"><strong>Select Custome=
r</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Choose an existing customer or left it blan=
k if u want create new customer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b64520cc-7851-459b-ba85-96535f4f4463">
<p local-id=3D"58ad735e-d85d-4741-a3e0-1496f173a98d"><strong>Customer Name<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Fill in relevant customer name (e.g., XYZ Co=
rp.).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b0ecbfa-11ba-4f55-b7d4-787280f73641">
<p local-id=3D"2d66d3ae-e5b8-4a8e-9ed1-448b95ed3c72"><strong>Customer</stro=
ng> <strong>Email </strong>=E2=80=93 (Optional) Fill in relevant customer e=
mail (e.g., admin@xyz.com).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9eeb0981-a072-4c6d-b5c4-9ec16241c294">
<p local-id=3D"f0a4087f-9f4d-4ecf-a72b-c54d4c1b63ca"><strong>Customer</stro=
ng> <strong>Phone </strong>=E2=80=93 (Optional) Fill in relevant customer p=
hone (e.g., +6287384748392).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e6f6b271-f7f1-4c52-a856-d04fd8fb5498">
<p local-id=3D"48d0adb1-b4b2-41ee-9906-cac7d2273b29"><strong><span class=3D=
"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"895346f5-000e-4674-bfbb-03f213f6c73d">C=
ustomer</span></strong> <strong>Address</strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Fill=
 in relevant customer address (e.g., Street Wall No.24).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de2cff7b-f558-4c78-ab47-29ac111aa32f">
<p local-id=3D"d323adba-7764-468a-80af-01137d5464ed">Add Multiple PIC (Max =
5 PIC). Each PIC includes the following fields:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4432b343-9e41-45f5-8e8c-a0a79454e0be">
<li local-id=3D"d85363c0-0eb6-45c2-8adf-bae458c74f71">
<p local-id=3D"e7fed89a-8f1b-452e-ae90-315984e79697"><strong>PIC Primary</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 Flag to mark as the primary PIC (<strong>only one</strong>=
 PIC should be primary).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ffdea39e-91f1-4ad6-bbb0-e67c04ece4ec">
<p local-id=3D"526bf9c9-d805-4bdf-9789-16baf8e73e59"><strong>PIC Name</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the PIC=E2=80=99s name (e.g., <em>John Doe<=
/em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4fb7aa02-cd01-4377-a84e-ea3463d2bcb2">
<p local-id=3D"1a2de179-b0ef-492d-bc06-708c52c6ea5a"><strong>PIC Email</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the PIC=E2=80=99s email (e.g., <a class=3D=
"external-link" href=3D"mailto:johndoe@mail.com" rel=3D"nofollow"><em>johnd=
oe@mail.com</em></a>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc8f0954-b0aa-466c-92be-b6e5a91c26ab">
<p local-id=3D"e22ef01f-7626-4298-97b6-c2e7b670d60d"><strong>PIC Phone</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the PIC=E2=80=99s phone number (e.g., <em>=
+6287384748392</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc8f0954-b0aa-466c-92be-b6e5a91c26ab">
<p local-id=3D"e22ef01f-7626-4298-97b6-c2e7b670d60d"><strong>PIC Role</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Select <em>Viewer</em> or <em>Approver</em>. This=
 determines actions allowed on the Microsite.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d4f2756-55f0-41e5-bc0d-42f6daecddfd">
<p local-id=3D"f6b854c0-2354-4489-887f-c907c5a8c924">Under <strong>Products=
</strong>, click <strong>Add Product</strong>:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5908e11a-da41-47ad-98e2-4806fad8766c">
<li local-id=3D"3446b4c8-e3b0-4292-b706-95feec82cb6d">
<p local-id=3D"a6bb1a47-f8d5-409c-b9f0-990daecfd78a">Select products.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"da84158b-3d07-4851-a3c8-779411ab44a3">
<p local-id=3D"6a45d953-9348-497d-821b-e7f18beac4ea">In the <strong>Add Pro=
duct to Quote</strong> popup:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac84aa93-0ee1-40c5-8aec-8faf4045d615">
<li local-id=3D"d70c39a0-636b-41d9-850d-e0164bb1b8ae">
<p local-id=3D"61e6d83b-abd7-45d5-8d71-f299237c2df0"><strong>Product</stron=
g> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Select or search for the product.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1266a7e-b4bc-48de-969b-273a59456a08">
<p local-id=3D"994314c4-90da-42e9-b153-fe4ecf1651b8"><strong>Quantity </str=
ong>=E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Input the number of units (e.g., 2).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8f63f13-3951-4fa8-b5e3-43a5eea3d21d">
<p local-id=3D"fe3fbf35-9069-4d91-b409-9724c5e1dde7"><strong>Attachments</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Upload up to 3 files (max 5 MB each).</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"ee9e4007-1dc7-411f-bcd1-1feb4dd46531">
<p local-id=3D"96bb0d52-c7a1-4d17-a8ec-1c6f73caf78b">(Optional) Upload rele=
vant <strong>Attachments</strong> such as product specifications or technic=
al drawings.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5e1414b-3a1f-48bb-9eed-afaf467d7f53">
<p local-id=3D"40b11a7a-9e39-41f3-b740-e185b2a39bf5">Add <strong>Additional=
 Information</strong>:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8ac37fcb-b4db-4fab-83bc-b6894fde444c">
<li local-id=3D"4b7d317b-a5fe-43ed-905d-adddc49ea4a4">
<p local-id=3D"04d9d02e-e437-4b38-a2e1-725dbbf8377c"><strong>Customer Notes=
 - </strong>(Optional)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc2dfdad-6e1a-48b5-b767-9ea28bf46717">
<p local-id=3D"e8d4de95-b664-4c82-8974-c45ab596a70c"><strong>Internal Notes=
</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Notes for internal team reference only.</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"76a8f620-e8ec-442b-9ec0-5255051e9073">
<p local-id=3D"ccf2bb29-2e09-4dd8-9785-a4b6d0815a48">Once completed, choose=
 one of the following actions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"97b508eb-e99d-4055-9048-7751889fce0d">
<li local-id=3D"e281dd53-5f0b-4cd1-aafa-c84faf765820">
<p local-id=3D"03cca69f-3c33-4786-b321-894aa27ca3e0"><strong>Save Draft</st=
rong> =E2=80=93 To continue editing later.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5dd13d72-4241-4d58-8b28-5d3d20784c74">
<p local-id=3D"a7b42a2c-d239-4392-9f47-4dcb77e07630"><strong>Submit</strong=
> =E2=80=93 To proceed for approval.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"e1897ed3-0c84-4b3e-9f1f-e9eb71510f0b" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-ApprovalFlow"><strong>Approval Flow</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"7963566f-5b68-4a33-9d1d-f4f0f9c1cea5">
<li local-id=3D"2fdb4459-823f-4d8c-aa83-74042bf085a2">
<p local-id=3D"b9641fc7-5968-498d-9c4e-310998509b6d">Submitted RFQs will fo=
llow the <strong>Approval Rules</strong> defined in the <strong>RFQ Setting=
s</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2edbcd9-7642-4c79-adf6-e7166da33946">
<p local-id=3D"36b67b57-b7e4-43fe-b97a-b3f11233f393">If no approval rule ex=
ists, the RFQ will be <strong>auto-approved</strong> and automatically move=
 to the <strong>Quotation</strong> stage.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"10f8bc10-f1d0-443d-9251-db4736ee3525">
<p local-id=3D"8ecdb2e1-0ce3-4f7c-94b3-6b744b2a3730">If approval is require=
d:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cf7ecb3e-028a-41e6-a970-0f5331352fd2">
<li local-id=3D"07aa9516-c3bb-4277-847f-5b8745581cf6">
<p local-id=3D"b94112fa-b050-4fa3-b9ea-66d416c0968f">The RFQ will be routed=
 to the designated approver.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df0885e2-6a86-4ea7-a7cf-d385f0d403b4">
<p local-id=3D"c72c2f67-8a8c-422e-8195-db7157d8d208">If <strong>approved</s=
trong>, it proceeds to <strong>Quotation</strong> creation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f6bf2059-b71d-4584-a33a-9addd4e87849">
<p local-id=3D"246322f9-f8ba-48aa-a0d8-9ba167517804">If <strong>rejected</s=
trong>, the RFQ cannot continue to the next stage.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"33eb4251-ca82-487d-b09c-38e98cc78f61">
<h3 local-id=3D"8b4d7e5e-501d-4b79-9cf6-4edf7b3edd43" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step7:ManageQuotes"><strong>Step 7: Manage Quotes</strong></h=
