<h3 local-id=3D"0eb792ca-c391-45b9-af7b-f7ff13dee460" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateaQuote"><strong>How to Create a Quote</strong></h3=
>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8e8715d8-c739-4f2d-af19-97cae693ed01">
<li local-id=3D"a0b96956-c058-4fae-bb58-9b8c196eb494">
<p local-id=3D"61f3972f-ad2d-4d7c-8677-ec6b46263e25"><strong>Navigate to</s=
trong> <code>Sales =E2=86=92 Quotes</code> in the sidebar.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"59407aa2-fbf5-44c4-95fb-82494b632683">
<p local-id=3D"76fa92a2-7447-442d-8967-778676f638ba"><strong>Click</strong>=
 <code>Create Quote</code> on the top-right corner.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cbcbcbca-b5ea-41a6-a080-c8610ec74b8b">
<p local-id=3D"18925b4e-393c-4241-baeb-7266fa4298f1"><strong>Fill Quote Det=
ails:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0457ca67-2a80-4ae1-b0f8-5d5ffee4309e">
<li local-id=3D"413714b4-c0e4-45ef-9db6-e9e2ade32059">
<p local-id=3D"78148e02-76fc-4245-bf9e-d01bea9d2a34"><strong>Currency</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 Select the transaction currency (e.g., IDR =E2=80=93 Indonesi=
an Rupiah).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fd84fbeb-3a7f-4eac-a5d4-fa61cd6b9f26">
<p local-id=3D"bf40b9af-ae8f-437d-a9f8-d882cd45161e"><strong>Down Payment P=
ercentage</strong> =E2=80=93 Define the required down payment (optional, de=
fault 0%).</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"73293067-146b-463e-bc83-348766b50b81">
<p local-id=3D"359a977e-97fa-4a5d-a05c-28badb0e5d81"><strong>Fill Customer =
Information:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"86720598-38e3-40a1-a0a2-d81b9404cf7d">
<li local-id=3D"0e02b27e-a092-4d49-a718-4fcddd5db729">
<p local-id=3D"8fe6683e-05e7-4a11-965d-bb010bcc84ec"><strong>Select Custome=
r</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Choose an existing customer or left it blan=
k if u want create new customer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e36d81c-ee66-426d-a322-008fd99ecd28">
<p local-id=3D"a43a0964-aaaa-453d-a03c-352bb6be2c92"><strong>Customer Name<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Fill in relevant customer name (e.g., XYZ Co=
rp.).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2693494-9b55-4659-ae42-ae91ee7cad2a">
<p local-id=3D"2fdd2e23-8368-4722-ae8d-0283ba65007e"><strong>Customer</stro=
ng> <strong>Email </strong>=E2=80=93 (Optional) Fill in relevant customer e=
mail (e.g., <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:admin@xyz.com" rel=3D=
"nofollow">admin@xyz.com</a>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"852126da-76ca-40cb-ac90-f6fd2800c5c0">
<p local-id=3D"fce6d2b1-00d1-4f57-a6b0-02c6f74b4d02"><strong>Customer</stro=
ng> <strong>Phone </strong>=E2=80=93 (Optional) Fill in relevant customer p=
hone (e.g., +6287384748392).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6df35017-6409-4cfb-b446-21d895056031">
<p local-id=3D"e5d28377-ba91-459f-8e0f-624adf7edf9a"><strong><span class=3D=
"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"b7c86df9-2ec9-43f2-af73-7fdf4cbf75bb">C=
ustomer</span></strong><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"b7=
c86df9-2ec9-43f2-af73-7fdf4cbf75bb"> </span><strong><span class=3D"inline-c=
omment-marker" data-ref=3D"b7c86df9-2ec9-43f2-af73-7fdf4cbf75bb">Address</s=
pan></strong><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"b7c86df9-2ec=
9-43f2-af73-7fdf4cbf75bb"> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Fill in relevant customer =
address (e.g., Street Wall No.24).</span></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e4a84f1-d360-47f8-ba69-9bfae893ccb8">
<p local-id=3D"4598d8ac-775a-414d-89cc-ebe732b02cfd">Add Multiple PIC (Max =
5 PIC). Each PIC includes the following fields:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd08df29-6a5a-4257-b7fd-62bca7d2035e">
<li local-id=3D"3d279acc-3a10-480e-8abd-c263ceac76a8">
<p local-id=3D"bb0d965c-e482-457c-ac2e-d49423f3763c"><strong>PIC Primary</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 Flag to mark as the primary PIC (<strong>only one</strong>=
 PIC should be primary).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46a95101-a013-4ea5-9855-7e2c232241da">
<p local-id=3D"1b0bd0c9-0f0c-4e14-8cf5-aaf518e79809"><strong>PIC Name</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the PIC=E2=80=99s name (e.g., <em>John Doe<=
/em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f67a77b-63aa-44fd-9560-92ac6b3d6d70">
<p local-id=3D"f6bd1845-aa17-473f-8632-897418863e4e"><strong>PIC Email</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the PIC=E2=80=99s email (e.g., <a class=3D=
"external-link" href=3D"mailto:johndoe@mail.com" rel=3D"nofollow"><em>johnd=
oe@mail.com</em></a>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4919bf5e-53fa-47b1-b752-b553bab22483">
<p local-id=3D"c0017477-9b89-4844-98e0-a7f7c15b017e"><strong>PIC Phone</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the PIC=E2=80=99s phone number (e.g., <em>=
+6287384748392</em>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4cebd526-b473-435c-91b5-e0fc1009e8b9">
<p local-id=3D"a1045758-a2a8-4b28-97db-638db27fcad5"><strong>PIC Role</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Select <em>Viewer</em> or <em>Approver</em>. This=
 determines actions allowed on the Microsite.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"9dcef726-dfb0-4d05-ad9b-4176ed2e99fe">
<p local-id=3D"41e5100c-8392-457a-8d56-2d3c6e1c711c"><strong>Add Products t=
o the Quote:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"031ac280-5971-499a-92b3-2a108b1317ae">
<li local-id=3D"402f479c-a264-43a2-b867-ab0540d7b20d">
<p local-id=3D"07817c99-dbd2-40f1-8ea0-6eea41edd185">Click <strong>+ Add Pr=
oduct</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"61175d92-baed-4ee6-b569-9c8901a62bc6">
<p local-id=3D"041defcc-4ba4-4f5a-9d25-a2650a766aa8">In the <strong>Add Pro=
duct to Quote</strong> popup:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2302b16b-160e-491b-af82-1396f8cbb798">
<li local-id=3D"4595cb3f-834d-45bf-b74c-00ff9cd61782">
<p local-id=3D"90b4e6d1-3e30-4002-8e0d-71c1e0aff2ce"><strong>Product</stron=
g> =E2=80=93 Select or search for the product.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"15c0433c-2d4f-4641-8ff5-bf3abb8a782f">
<p local-id=3D"e50ec5bd-9988-4030-9405-5d4f29212f36"><strong>Quantity </str=
ong>=E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Input the number of units (e.g., 2)..</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b5f196d-9942-429d-a5b0-626d719281ce">
<p local-id=3D"4882ed1f-fbd1-4c58-bbf1-2e7b5b3b31dd"><strong>Unit Price </s=
trong>=E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Enter the price per unit (e.g., IDR 200.000)..<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"442dd6cc-13b6-40a2-9f6a-8003c6f06698">
<p local-id=3D"ca8b05f7-7dad-4f4d-8a9d-92588fa2d760"><strong>Discount </str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Add a discount if applicable (e.g., 0%).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"62ffca4e-83c6-466d-9a98-de3f5b34cb9f">
<p local-id=3D"0084337e-dd7d-4930-aea5-59c320260b31"><strong>Total Price</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 Automatically calculated based on quantity and discount (e=
.g., IDR 200.000).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b45398b-549d-48c5-aed7-c4990a989c68">
<p local-id=3D"6e03ecb2-54c4-47c6-b6ed-2e474364c885"><strong>Notes</strong>=
 =E2=80=93 (Optional) Add internal or customer notes.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c84b18d-8078-436d-a7ab-8c2e5a9dcfa4">
<p local-id=3D"725a0fbd-84ee-4848-9988-584ac39021da"><strong>Attachments</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Upload up to 3 files (max 5 MB each), such as =
product specs documents.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"17071806-6133-47cd-ac37-328d74b3bc72">
<p local-id=3D"f4539fce-7b5c-4cff-960b-968bca35ec94"><strong>Total Amount:<=
/strong><br>
After products are added, the system automatically calculates totals. Compl=
ete the following fields:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0f17857d-3260-4f81-bb5a-e7a4910b4d68">
<li local-id=3D"6ea4221f-505d-4258-b998-5f6e5941e19e">
<p local-id=3D"1de40b2d-fa12-48bd-afa8-91cc6482ebcc"><strong>Subtotal</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 Total before taxes or fees (e.g., IDR 200.000)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44ab8cc3-0ee4-49d2-a7fd-4b15308267ff">
<p local-id=3D"bbfd7876-840f-48ca-9e3e-e2af1626d9be"><strong>Tax Rate </str=
ong>=E2=80=93 (Optional) Input tax rate (e.g., 10%).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f847c033-0a3a-41c5-bc5b-eafa9a6a9441">
<p local-id=3D"7379d257-6d12-465b-97b7-bd8a86ef0264"><strong>Tax Total</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 Total updates automatically. (e.g., IDR 20.000)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4388f4d7-63ee-41c4-94f1-d42396397e80">
<p local-id=3D"8f1d2288-aeab-4e2a-a691-c3ea59de20f2"><strong>Shipping Fee</=
strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Optional shipping cost. (e.g., IDR 10.000)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"ef5eb548-fd2d-40d4-a712-6272396c0fce">
<p local-id=3D"8c3f23a9-0cc2-4f69-8169-46d3505cb8f4"><strong>Other Fee</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Add additional charges if any. (e.g., IDR 20.000)=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4661c10-c62c-4d5a-95d0-c534871043bf">
<p local-id=3D"13d5057a-616a-4023-b437-267c43665381"><strong>Total</strong>=
 =E2=80=93 Final amount after tax and all fees. (e.g., IDR 250.000)</p></li=
>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e944e2aa-419e-4928-aadd-17dc9b131383">
<p local-id=3D"b7e79e89-aa1d-4e6f-9bdb-a50f821686c5"><strong>Add Attachment=
s (Optional):</strong><br>
Upload general files related to the quotation, such as proposals, photos, o=
r supporting documents.<br>
You can upload up to 3 files (max 5 MB each).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"837a68f9-2a65-4ded-91f4-fb0e5a2523df">
<p local-id=3D"8a73a0cc-1f28-46e1-9407-7068839a532e"><strong>Fill Terms &am=
p; Conditions:</strong><br></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrap=
per image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"con=
fluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20251010-070203.png" widt=
h=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"8d4a79e6196f8f9952a880be85c5eadf4566905de=
1cff0e2b2c9b08ddf658128" data-image-src=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.=
net/wiki/download/attachments/1464336406/image-20251010-070203.png?version=
=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1760079726793&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2=
" data-height=3D"586" data-width=3D"2752" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"=
0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1471053832" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1=
" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-ali=
as=3D"image-20251010-070203.png" data-base-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atl=
assian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linke=
d-resource-container-id=3D"1464336406" data-linked-resource-container-versi=
on=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"bb292aba-ff87-4a1d-8869-fba18de640d6" data-media=
-type=3D"file" height=3D"99"></span>
<p local-id=3D"1584015d-82a4-4147-944f-b0964e109308"><br>
Define agreement details before submission:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a20d58db-d434-47bf-b9d6-936d4cc092d8">
<li local-id=3D"1e68b909-cf6b-452a-807a-4b174c6e3033">
<p local-id=3D"fef1ad8f-ef8f-4418-a276-c6ca2c5b6e11"><strong>Payment Terms<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 (Mandatory) Select available payment options (e.g., NET =
30 =E2=80=93 payment due in 30 days after invoice, NET 60, or Cash Before D=
elivery).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2eaf7691-4e3a-41ff-bbb5-c5b795ca91c1">
<p local-id=3D"082406ba-3eab-415a-9346-a2acbe93cc91"><strong>Incoterms</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Select delivery terms if applicable (e.g., FOB =
=E2=80=93 Free on Board, CIF =E2=80=93 Cost, Insurance, and Freight, or EXW=
 =E2=80=93 Ex Works).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73ddfc4b-1e05-41fb-b9e1-00a6e207babc">
<p local-id=3D"7bff0fc3-aef8-409b-872e-58388e16d90f"><strong>Risk Level</st=
rong> =E2=80=93 Automatically filled with the project or transaction risk l=
evel based on the selected Incoterms (e.g., Medium Risk for international s=
hipment using CIF terms).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99ebb541-717f-40ab-adc4-1c44ad2ccd37">
<p local-id=3D"75293bef-a02e-4ce5-b2b7-a14aa1cd8bde"><strong>Estimated Deli=
very</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Input expected delivery time (e.g., 2=E2=
=80=933 weeks after order confirmation).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71c4c522-f77a-42f1-a6c8-2ac746c168bc">
<p local-id=3D"bfda8ceb-16a9-4549-a167-0f08147d2c40"><strong>Governing Law<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Define applicable law or jurisdiction (e.g., =
Indonesian Law or Singapore Commercial Law).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3754e779-aa7f-4a15-a76c-7df5f9dcd8ac">
<p local-id=3D"6aa5526b-aec9-4686-be51-2a0be92182af"><strong>Shipping Metho=
d</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Choose the transportation method (e.g., Air=
 Freight, Sea Cargo, or Local Courier).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4cbde405-748a-48fa-8bed-1eb8b5dfedfd">
<p local-id=3D"6984d28f-2f6c-43a1-9545-06330a268abd"><strong>Dispute Resolu=
tion Method</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Define how disputes will be resol=
ved (e.g., Arbitration, Mediation, or Court Settlement).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3375e41-1b17-4a22-ba21-30aceea8e2a8">
<p local-id=3D"e4f08962-534f-49a5-9583-87b54ae430fb"><strong>Include Clause=
s (Optional):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed5a8ef1-f13e-477b-a590-676b355eba68">
<li local-id=3D"5b740470-b847-4118-b486-d56694766d34">
<p local-id=3D"ba7c409f-9101-4976-b71e-cbbe6ffe3117"><strong>Include Force =
Majeure Clause</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Protects both parties if unexp=
ected events (e.g., disasters) prevent fulfillment of the agreement.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"f28933a4-9230-452c-b552-2f187d575b80">
<p local-id=3D"45b6ed44-21cf-4581-ac26-84cfec49901b"><strong>Include Late P=
ayment Penalties</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Applies fees or interest if =
the customer pays past the due date.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dd8c20bf-6ed2-42a9-82f1-a2f8242eaa26">
<p local-id=3D"53ba8d2d-5299-49d9-87fb-dbac905a9e60"><strong>Include Perfor=
mance Guarantees</strong> =E2=80=93 (Optional) Ensures the seller meets agr=
eed quality or delivery standards.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"66ad929c-ff7e-4abd-99bd-d76379468c6e">
<p local-id=3D"3cfb6e2f-2eb3-4c7e-91fe-435b108992c5"><strong>Final Actions:=
</strong><br>
After filling all required details:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"21ce4585-82e3-4507-b338-78133f21982d">
<li local-id=3D"aef9f380-ca7c-475f-9952-38bad3757356">
<p local-id=3D"60ce5d25-d8e1-4b6e-8584-c9d4ede866ea"><strong>Save Draft</st=
rong> =E2=80=93 Save for later editing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"648e0830-b12e-434d-84cd-97134516ed00">
<p local-id=3D"1b9c0bc8-657c-4fb8-9e8e-89d60c9782ca"><strong>Submit</strong=
> =E2=80=93 Send the quotation for approval.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"f572aa96-c794-4ffd-938f-782c850c5111" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Notes:.4">Notes:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2ee11167-16df-4d28-80b8-1b17f22fa31e">
<li local-id=3D"b09d2dad-3817-47f4-9be4-4004c2f4f21c">
<p local-id=3D"11268ddf-f563-47bb-ae41-e6385a96fafd"><span class=3D"inline-=
comment-marker" data-ref=3D"602e60e6-4875-42bd-b08d-5f0a044f341a">If you wa=
nt to use a currency other than your base currency, please ensure your </sp=
an><strong>FX Management</strong> module is updated. You must input the <st=
rong>latest FX exchange rate</strong> to ensure accurate conversion during =
quotation.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c8f58f8c-6e65-4b5e-ae49-a944efe053bf" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-QuoteStatusFlow"><strong>Quote Status Flow</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"9a3110d4-1e82-4de2-80ee-38dd9a3208e3">
<li local-id=3D"1b56e1cf-27fd-46af-b2c9-0a5e3f066f95">
<p local-id=3D"e9005733-5033-4fbd-aa9b-120169618d4b"><strong>Draft</strong>=
 =E2=80=93 Quotation is being prepared and not yet submitted.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e911737-7d6f-4403-9ec5-dc10c3837d9f">
<p local-id=3D"75510a2d-65d1-48a6-9ba2-4b9ebb640d2d"><strong>Submitted</str=
ong> =E2=80=93 Waiting for internal approval (based on approval rules).</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"f42f21d7-d6c4-4375-a149-f991938b17f3">
<p local-id=3D"75e88b12-0dab-41fe-ad4e-a9b28b87c20e"><strong>Issued</strong=
> =E2=80=93 Approved internally and sent to the customer.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2470feb6-7be2-4e4a-93e0-147b68acc125">
<p local-id=3D"65fae17f-ffc9-4276-ad11-f3dcdc0b1e27"><strong>Approved</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 Customer has accepted the quotation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05e04bbf-5b70-42b3-9f9a-02ecbd7ec869">
<p local-id=3D"4e70daca-c17d-403f-ab91-c23eaf316d08"><strong>Rejected</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 Rejected by internal approver or customer.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13196bf2-ccee-4c51-bed5-69908d8bcfe8">
<p local-id=3D"c60cfc51-7a3f-4f82-8196-d4927e2f461b"><strong>Need Revision<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 Customer requested updates or corrections before approva=
l.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5abf3c4a-d433-4878-8f34-bcdaee70d61d" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-ApprovalFlow.1"><strong>Approval Flow</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"999a14c8-4b0a-40d3-94b4-64c861429637">
<li local-id=3D"343f0a02-c573-408b-ba83-ce7d0ce73a72">
<p local-id=3D"59c0357d-e4ce-4cda-a380-c433dd95a13c">Internal approval foll=
ows the rules defined in <strong>Quote Settings =E2=86=92 Approval Rules</s=
trong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5242c3b4-0771-41b6-b94e-5180d8b27b89">
<p local-id=3D"c744d238-79fb-4e5b-8a55-17eaba0a4cda">Once internally approv=
ed, the quote changes to <strong>Issued</strong> and awaits customer approv=
al.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"685cd371-344e-40da-b037-a96381872a6d">
<p local-id=3D"cc3a063e-ea9f-4d87-a158-63cc06c1661d">The customer must appr=
ove before the quote can be converted into an <strong>Order</strong>.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"fc335ffe-e37c-483d-8cc2-49065a0a252d">
<p local-id=3D"9cc68234-8ae1-4dd1-a892-b94bd0ce306e">If no approval rule ex=
ists, the system automatically moves from <strong>Submitted =E2=86=92 Issue=
d</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"feb8fe06-a0a3-4e0c-bf7b-183abf14d9f5" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-AfterApproval"><strong>After Approval</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c615ed18-63c5-44ed-8782-5225e6cdc4dd">
<li local-id=3D"fc17a2e9-e6f4-4b89-9874-c80ac3cc2e8c">
<p local-id=3D"bf6db815-15c8-479b-9e9f-9c8e22abafe7">Once <strong>Approved<=
/strong> by the customer:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cf38e0cc-8f49-4190-a00c-fbda833780a0">
<li local-id=3D"a16c60e1-fd45-491a-ad8f-a016468dee77">
<p local-id=3D"fce87e47-d5e7-44cb-b82a-72b53a965160">The system automatical=
ly converts the quote into an <strong>Order and Work Order</strong>.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"e61cec74-617c-4ce8-9fb6-820e8714f2a7">
<p local-id=3D"13279ff3-e04d-468c-8f27-1c711125f9f1">All pricing, product, =
and payment details are carried forward.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"896d4852-2853-44e5-ac16-0e22cbd081b5">
<p local-id=3D"ac981505-2327-4f7c-97b7-09be43aa2c6f">If Downpayment is fill=
ed, system will automatically create Downpayment Invoice.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"75ef6267-2824-4d88-beb8-7881a2cf9947">
<p local-id=3D"6e61d1e8-b582-4239-9351-0ae678d85285"><strong>Rejected</stro=
ng> quotes cannot proceed to the next stage.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d3cc125d-ea7d-4c31-ab08-270640769373">
<h3 local-id=3D"c762b493-7b65-49fe-bc2d-08c49b926523" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step8:ManageOrders">Step 8: Manage Orders</h3>
<p local-id=3D"707db157-0808-4620-ab86-a7ba34c85d3a">Confirm and manage cus=
tomer orders to proceed with manufacturing and shipment. You can also updat=
e order details, attach documents, and track related invoices, work orders,=
 and shipment records.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"ef9bb250-1b50-42d1-8b6a-4b7fc3c2fcdd" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoViewOrders">How to View Orders</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"bcc25b5f-038a-47a5-867a-969bca812f8e">
<li local-id=3D"1ee3a5d6-fee1-4211-a5fc-53ff22535e9c">
<p local-id=3D"d1f7ae74-7965-4763-ab2b-571dce7170c5">Navigate to Procuremen=
t =E2=86=92 Orders.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b3a4bece-fecb-47ea-9197-e206a7330949">
<p local-id=3D"c0addac9-14c7-485e-9258-c7508e6c293a">Select the desired Ord=
er from the list to open the Order Details page.</p></li>
</ol>
