<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"3690b17f-8fc6-4e2a-9529-6ec2a1463211">
<li local-id=3D"687dffc8-6bce-4769-8b55-32959baecfb2">
<p local-id=3D"0e8110ff-1eea-4345-93ca-d874f4365c0f">On the Order Details p=
age, click Edit in the top-right corner.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfe2d6d7-dcdf-440b-8896-53413a572b69">
<p local-id=3D"1067b91f-670e-4fe0-bde7-f55564d6e3c1">You can update the fol=
lowing fields:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"73bcf42d-f56a-4526-a679-801e6c178eb7">
<li local-id=3D"16941a64-a0e5-4014-9980-0408b6ef1b6b">
<p local-id=3D"c161f0e7-9a00-4c07-bc4c-5813ba7e7159"><strong>Planned Start =
Date</strong> =E2=80=93 Input the target start date for the order (e.g., 15=
 Oct 2025).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29fa21ca-1fcf-45fc-ab28-29ff905d34b4">
<p local-id=3D"6e594025-d6c8-4273-9da5-6e0006279fd8"><strong>Planned End Da=
te</strong> =E2=80=93 Input the estimated completion date for the order (e.=
g., 25 Oct 2025).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"60dc440e-1626-4a4e-bf1a-6887e6a29c0a">
<p local-id=3D"d9489531-ad36-4c22-8461-7a26eaf671f6"><strong>Actual Start D=
ate</strong> =E2=80=93 Record the actual date when the order process begins=
 (e.g., 16 Oct 2025).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"30c93132-7a19-4070-a00f-ba0ad0d78e79">
<p local-id=3D"8e284fb8-bf40-4c12-a974-0ed3d94d0ca2"><strong>Actual End Dat=
e</strong> =E2=80=93 Record the actual date when the order process is compl=
eted (e.g., 24 Oct 2025).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88260ac4-abb6-4acc-8901-139a6ac6c132">
<p local-id=3D"0a17220c-bc86-436e-b8b8-9c334170c15d"><strong>Priority</stro=
ng> =E2=80=93 Define the priority level of the order (e.g., Low, Medium, Hi=
gh, or Urgent).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7dcfa102-725d-4889-848f-4760da5d13fb">
<p local-id=3D"802d6f30-e544-4bc4-b632-95db16e7611b"><strong>Remarks</stron=
g> =E2=80=93 Add any additional notes or important information related to t=
he order (e.g., =E2=80=9CExpedite delivery due to customer request=E2=80=9D=
).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c3af1f72-d17c-47bc-9e10-6863f5b5a357">
<p local-id=3D"5c0b48ee-6b31-4c7f-8855-1db4ef5c4869"><strong>Purchase Order=
 No</strong> =E2=80=93 PO number provided by the buyer.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"290c5c22-cafa-41db-b9d3-b4b07448a18e">
<p local-id=3D"afdf6637-2967-424a-8a4d-bd12b2bf01f9">You can also add Attac=
hments related to the order (e.g., additional files, supporting documents).=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"516981bb-fe50-484e-b21f-a30b3ceeaa54">
<p local-id=3D"37e58991-dce4-494d-960f-9b77e125f154">Click Save to confirm =
changes.</p></li>
</ol>
