<p local-id=3D"b4b3311e-128c-4c4a-ba86-c62136fc37cd">You can view and manag=
e shipment records for tracking and documentation purposes.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a5420a9b-872a-4b91-a0e6-75a98e6dc8af">Note: Shipment records=
 here are for documentation and reference only.</p></li>
