<h3 local-id=3D"681959f3-5542-45fb-9912-0981cfa6b84f" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-OrderStatusFlow">Order Status Flow</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"b98f9697-dbe4-4811-8d73-35086df2de15">
<li local-id=3D"2f060bf7-4b3a-4d22-8a39-ce06e8481ed3">
<p local-id=3D"7e7fa625-a997-4656-bf14-7ff81952feae">Not Started =E2=80=93 =
Order has been created but not yet processed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f7d9cdf-2199-4ce0-a404-532ee2baf722">
<p local-id=3D"4d9950ca-4fae-4a9b-b015-da178b177433">Waiting for Approval =
=E2=80=93 Pending internal approval based on approval rules.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0027bd3-b707-489a-aa2e-660f6f67ecf8">
<p local-id=3D"9987a946-8b18-4dae-a937-2ebab98d2c63">Confirmed =E2=80=93 Or=
der has been approved and is ready for manufacturing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86597779-2003-446a-9cd6-74e6c17f2093">
<p local-id=3D"1089a3dc-ba7c-4380-a96a-ddb1e91d146a">In Progress =E2=80=93 =
Work Order related to this Order is ongoing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3e8e0276-744c-45d5-aad9-f1b417c120df">
<p local-id=3D"9de8104f-9250-4f97-8f1a-940367d0a2da">Ready to Ship =E2=80=
=93 All Work Orders under this Order are finished and Ready to ship.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"7ebf2b6c-159d-42e9-b5aa-8b5cd182f998">
<p local-id=3D"f6c5f650-ccb1-453b-b200-910296288096">On Shipping - On going=
 Shipping</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a91ef959-edf0-4374-81af-a2e2e3e31019">
<p local-id=3D"b49baa92-c475-4f3c-9d64-d80c96192dcb">Completed =E2=80=93 Al=
l processes are complete, and the final invoice has been fully paid.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"b572c9d8-6e1e-4633-9386-12490edcc593">
<p local-id=3D"26213beb-c04e-4a1f-bac6-42a5ab9dbc47">Canceled =E2=80=93 Ord=
er has been rejected or canceled.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"ef80b0fb-65e7-4d57-a033-e1c0d9453c40" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-ApprovalFlow.2">Approval Flow</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"42822f9e-78d1-45ff-9304-7c4a58d86d48">
<li local-id=3D"afbd3e89-a4ca-4bec-ab0b-cd915655e374">
<p local-id=3D"02528b1e-0b4d-46aa-b385-b6a7ac482b1d">Follows approval rules=
 defined in Order Settings =E2=86=92 Approval Rules.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"349036f6-4f06-4271-8643-3d79530bc064">
<p local-id=3D"d136d16c-e7a4-4d1f-8329-9e3c8d9732e2">Once approved, the Ord=
er status changes from Waiting for Approval =E2=86=92 Confirmed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5600fad4-afad-4ca3-a609-672fb9f5eae4">
<p local-id=3D"6f2dc6b8-5f8f-42e6-b33a-be29281a60e3">If no approval rule ex=
ists, the Order will move directly from Not Started =E2=86=92 Confirmed.</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"275f9797-0eff-4a4b-953e-c41db3bbaf8e">
<h3 local-id=3D"8514904c-2bd0-4019-b69c-dfec22828379" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step9:ManageWorkOrder"><strong>Step 9: Manage Work Order</str=
ong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"d8e5f1bc-e49a-459c-aec0-feea4c9a0a77">Start the production p=
rocess based on your Bill of Materials (BOM) and Routing. Work Orders is au=
tomatically created once the Quote is approved by the customer along with t=
he Order creation. Work Order can only be started when the Order is Confirm=
ed and the materials are allocated.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"9f8e954e-e767-4980-a1e6-4d104a612d80" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoViewWorkOrders">How to View Work Orders</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"c3a61b5b-a633-4689-b989-99b23570c71d">
<li local-id=3D"56e363a8-b58a-4d16-aad6-7ce35219a9ea">
<p local-id=3D"ce76cfa2-d1cc-4867-8310-5b94303e75b1">Navigate to Procuremen=
t =E2=86=92 Work Orders.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef2e09d1-c067-4b99-9d8b-bddf97be8660">
<p local-id=3D"8fee5e88-c615-4708-bccb-2b088472f878">Select the desired Wor=
k Order from the list to open the Work Order Detail page.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"f3425358-3bb0-43fe-aeab-6cdbcd2e92b1" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoAllocateMaterials">How to Allocate Materials</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6378a25e-3413-4a2f-8143-f2461af61ce0">Before production star=
ts, materials must be available in the inventory.</p><span class=3D"conflue=
nce-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-s=
ize"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-202=
51010-082914.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"8ae6d69dae564ceae6b=
1ed26c3d0dee55f8387eed0f4877988f4d5232a01bfb8" data-image-src=3D"https://sc=
vcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1464336406/image-202510=
10-082914.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1760084958938&amp;cacheVer=
sion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1378" data-width=3D"2668" data-unreso=
lved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1471709196" data-linked=
-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linke=
d-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-082914.png" data-base-url=3D"htt=
ps://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D=
"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1464336406" data-linked-re=
source-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"a525690e-a7b2-4237-b696-01=
7635f911f8" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"241"></span>
<p local-id=3D"8d498ad6-3bf4-405f-9c6a-48b7f6679ef3">To allocate materials:=
</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"a60ff9cc-3010-4cfb-b58b-3a8585c89d96">
<li local-id=3D"9c23294a-1f86-4fdd-905d-475f43305803">
<p local-id=3D"902a8c7c-69c3-4561-84ea-994360c4a076">Open the desired Work =
Order.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdbdff19-6403-4c6f-8086-87bb816d0c5f">
<p local-id=3D"a825da02-6d60-4758-b6cf-0030430331a5">Click Ready to Process=
 (manual process from Order page) or it will be set automatically if the Or=
der is already confirmed =E2=80=94 this will display the Allocate Materials=
 button.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f65f3595-5967-4966-9f7c-060c5f7adb83">
<p local-id=3D"c0a40395-f08a-4fea-a4aa-4fbf2f243a30">Click Allocate Materia=
ls.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a64325cc-06d3-4737-aae4-daeedbb8bfe8">
<p local-id=3D"60446f39-0d56-4d9e-a0a4-f89953b62cbd">The system will show a=
 confirmation:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"af77f30f-abbe-4ad0-9795-b36dfbbb5f97">
<li local-id=3D"4d180133-ba12-42a4-b379-594a380afbf5">
<p local-id=3D"b34b8e24-6fc8-4988-b06b-16d7783dff9d">If sufficient stock =
=E2=86=92 the system allocates materials and shows a success message.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"5fa199ef-61c6-45ec-b71a-05748fe576b9">
<p local-id=3D"180f2cfc-6585-404f-b73d-e344587d8d86">If insufficient stock =
=E2=86=92 the system displays an error and cannot allocate.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"5a804b53-0796-42a3-b9eb-9160287e4ca0">Notes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fcfe8daf-dab8-4d64-b194-498387af91a9">
<li local-id=3D"d83616dc-8947-4b55-acd9-6f3449a2e695">
<p local-id=3D"57282c45-9d68-4525-83b6-f8aa823c12d8">You cannot start produ=
ction without allocation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"443d33f2-67ec-4379-a9c9-8b6768244c24">
<p local-id=3D"bfe75e01-9a21-4662-a984-0c8c4ac2f0e5">The Allocate Materials=
 button only appears when the status is Ready to Process.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"4f4f2666-70b7-49a2-9d2a-4ac43df42037" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoManageRoutingStages">How to Manage Routing Stages</h3>
<p local-id=3D"be7b6c60-2b02-4f99-a1cc-6a5b25c19e23">After successful mater=
ial allocation, you can manage and track progress for each Routing Stage.</=
p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper conf=
luence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-=
center" alt=3D"image-20251010-083044.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" sr=
c=3D"5b79e84e92d947eb019a424f2695df492f5f77de527d5a0f494cd5676ed2b3cf" data=
-image-src=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments=
/1464336406/image-20251010-083044.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17=
60085048580&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1356" data-wi=
dth=3D"2700" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D=
"1471217674" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=
=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-083044=
.png" data-base-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linke=
d-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"=
1464336406" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"=
de678c7f-b1dc-4308-91ed-8c420ba513ea" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"23=
4"></span>
<p local-id=3D"e3bb8274-0cfa-4fcd-8650-b51907ae3d56"></p>
<p local-id=3D"cb85422d-4b0b-4670-b531-eaa0563134ff">To update routing prog=
ress:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8d15cecd-0a1e-427e-ac38-40e6b263e5ab">
<li local-id=3D"769ea149-1614-49bb-be9e-7e3626a46ea5">
<p local-id=3D"ac2a1fce-6b5d-42c4-9ec5-c09c8cc866db">Go to the Routing Stag=
es tab inside the Work Order.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f6077cc8-7c5e-4340-9e39-5a9d7e75e967">
<p local-id=3D"60a25906-7968-40a4-9f5e-6751ad06f140">For each stage, click =
Manage.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"697f68c0-b5a7-4605-b01b-ef0ca02c0c94">
<p local-id=3D"2896ccc4-07af-4a16-a5a2-b13eab41c96c">Update the quantities =
for Yet to Start, In Progress, or Completed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"20488230-6d5d-4566-949d-ce865ecdb5c5">
<p local-id=3D"430a2fe5-b455-440c-b096-6eaa61f1e3c5">Click Save Progress.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2f64e31-2231-4f56-86e8-ca5c8cac2137">
<p local-id=3D"16b9d14a-dfec-4ed1-bda3-391cb7ce4751">The system automatical=
ly calculates progress percentage.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"9bc8a8cb-2d72-4d9c-9a46-011e9416d16b">Notes:<br>
Routing stages can only be managed after successful material allocation.<br=
>
Updating progress in any routing stage will automatically change the status=
 to In Progress.<br>
Alternatively, you can manually click the Start Process button to begin.</p=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"d114c9bb-ccde-461e-912f-7d47e551a1e9" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCompleteWorkOrder">How to Complete Work Order</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5dd766ac-2ed0-4377-bead-03cb16b974e5">Once all routing stage=
s are completed, mark the production as finished.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8b8037f7-d4e6-4654-8925-91fc94f65ba1">To complete:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8518c9bf-7942-4021-b8f7-150af94f9035">
<li local-id=3D"f0f838c3-36ce-4a44-b52c-71891d041f3e">
<p local-id=3D"e4fe4e5b-a993-4d60-8464-4fd76d58881f">Verify that all routin=
g stages are 100% completed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65cfafc4-618b-4bd4-87d8-75040558f2d9">
<p local-id=3D"7f49372c-feca-4fac-a4b9-bcfd7b77b046">Click Complete Work Or=
der.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77ead4be-9331-4ffa-98e5-37ea553d79fa">
<p local-id=3D"33450953-dca5-4a46-9706-67a2ef699248">Confirm the completion=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a8a6c081-1154-4395-8aa0-24ce8c7fe910">
<p local-id=3D"c4a6e947-6db3-4bee-b1c0-fae1615c28dc">The Work Order status =
will change to Completed, and finished goods will be updated in inventory.<=
/p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"e0a32209-9f0a-4ff2-8076-bd1493b8e6c2" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-WorkOrderStatusFlow">Work Order Status Flow</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"357c7fbd-44d2-428e-9971-93a1ea45dc97">
<li local-id=3D"8138a457-9ba3-4001-a1b5-62902495cb46">
<p local-id=3D"ca8ae6da-8ccb-49ab-9618-fb25625509dc">Not Started =E2=86=92 =
Work Order created but not yet processed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3012c359-35de-4c26-a582-34aa098195b0">
<p local-id=3D"13758963-6322-4e0a-9bab-3ca6181b7d40">Ready to Process =E2=
=86=92 Materials allocated and ready for production.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"239d124d-1fcc-4af8-8936-6435653a0951">
<p local-id=3D"dd80a4f8-70c9-4c67-a875-e94b31a4913b">In Progress =E2=86=92 =
Routing stages are ongoing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e49788e7-4e30-4f16-8317-101b49de7ada">
<p local-id=3D"1836aa25-e4ec-4f5a-8ece-dd745e3b10d9">Completed =E2=86=92 Al=
l stages are finished; goods updated in inventory.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"112ab677-3975-42f2-b169-00624e00a907">
<p local-id=3D"024a105d-a2f2-44cd-8f9a-edae2da983d4">Canceled =E2=86=92 Wor=
k Order terminated or voided before completion.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"69e39280-301a-4c2b-97d3-80b573ed8e52">
<h3 local-id=3D"94b55bad-0482-48a5-b0dd-5bf1b3cec359" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-Step10:CreateInvoice"><strong>Step 10: Create Invoice</strong=
></h3>
<p local-id=3D"82382fc2-06ce-46e0-9ce9-a42b2d1343d2">A <strong> Invoice</st=
rong> can be created either from the <strong>Order Detail</strong> page or =
directly from the <strong>Invoice</strong> menu. This allows users to recor=
d repayment / down payment transactions linked to specific orders.</p><span=
 class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-=
embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center"=
 alt=3D"image-20251010-083359.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"9c=
dd1ee61da60170885d643cc5f0197246e333469aa249dedef1038a7b82c9e1" data-image-=
src=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/146433=
6406/image-20251010-083359.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D176008524=
2975&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1346" data-width=3D"=
2658" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"147157=
8137" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attac=
hment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251010-083359.png" dat=
a-base-url=3D"https://scvcashenable.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resourc=
e-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"146433640=
6" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"10" data-media-id=3D"63a5564b-=
7a4d-4230-908f-0cbf400ae7ce" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"236"></span=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"cf00b783-7ac0-433b-8456-770611518488" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-FromOrderDetail"><strong>From Order Detail</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"7705c50a-5340-4f1b-a77e-7c4e40de7f01">
<li local-id=3D"d188cb43-2315-43a7-866b-4e76261bacff">
<p local-id=3D"378ae87a-be73-48c0-a5ae-97b595710bc8">Navigate to the desire=
d <strong>Order</strong> page.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"571b7030-4e19-4bad-8a1e-0ef205aef916">
<p local-id=3D"7cf79709-497b-4dcb-8f86-de8f3ced79a4">In the <strong>Invoice=
s</strong> section, click <strong>Add Invoice</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f637af4e-9c7e-48b6-af50-3c6bd59ed0b5">
<p local-id=3D"f2e516a7-1c20-47f7-83fc-cbdf73967402">Select the <strong>Inv=
oice Type</strong> as <em>Repayment</em>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16730752-b846-498e-be99-0077d440f2fb">
<p local-id=3D"bb5bec1d-e429-4d60-a09f-e26b131e58ee">The <strong>Order Numb=
er</strong> will be filled in automatically.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"38e624e3-4b09-405b-b2aa-d25fa7418cf1">
<p local-id=3D"c77dd493-1db2-4b6b-9265-9fc1c0cdedb5">Click <strong>Save</st=
rong> to create the repayment invoice.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"c3363041-db7e-4e7b-9971-8a60799e8e5e" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-FromInvoicePage"><strong>From Invoice Page</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"38dc8fd7-9218-49d7-927a-0b9b3c8af850">
<li local-id=3D"2efd25ed-e19c-415b-bda6-59854a1a2a7b">
<p local-id=3D"b52203bf-e5ed-45b9-9d7c-65fba9ebba78">Navigate to <strong>Fi=
nance =E2=86=92 Invoices</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"17eeb838-1ed6-42a2-b32a-caf054baa84a">
<p local-id=3D"fdb48852-430f-47a1-a447-4699bb030194">Click <strong>Create I=
nvoice</strong> on the top-right corner.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1266c75-a48d-4911-95fd-4e9bdaa02812">
<p local-id=3D"faf240e5-dd56-4a79-afb8-1b2412540eb0">Choose the <strong>Inv=
oice Type</strong> as <em>Repayment</em>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ca7225c-ad07-441f-976e-0ec8331df420">
<p local-id=3D"09d17f5a-b1a7-45cf-919d-7931668c8dd1">Select or input the <s=
trong>Order Number</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83d943f3-bc8c-43c5-9e52-f42d1e90af86">
<p local-id=3D"fe69aa2a-307a-4280-b08e-15173e668dab">Click <strong>Save</st=
rong> to complete the creation.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"0fdec39f-9670-40d9-b136-9d683f3e42ce">
<h2 local-id=3D"6e7b6231-ffd6-4c6f-9deb-c3317b4d3ab6" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-UserManagementSetting"><strong>User Management Setting</stron=
g></h2>
<p local-id=3D"e09cda79-c66d-48a4-82e1-a35563524254">The <strong>User Manag=
ement</strong> module allows administrators to manage user groups, assign p=
ermissions, and control access to specific menus and actions within the sys=
tem.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"01f1a6c2-2ab2-4ce4-a2e0-a7dc4d7e5c98" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoViewUserGroupList"><strong>How to View User Group List</=
strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2fedabf5-8242-4009-80e1-15058dac0ad5">
<li local-id=3D"bb06ed7c-8f60-4d3d-b017-641625b1f96f">
<p local-id=3D"096cffbc-e2fb-4c72-9b13-c6911ff458d6">Navigate to <strong>Ad=
ministration =E2=86=92 User Management =E2=86=92 Groups</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b03ecfb-da94-4483-9db4-31e1030c255f">
<p local-id=3D"7442c904-f412-458c-a1ad-be3edc512560">The system displays a =
list of all existing user groups.</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"547092b0-f92d-4b3a-a3c7-111ca125b380" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoCreateUserGroup"><strong>How to Create User Group</stron=
g></h3><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper=
