<h3 local-id=3D"35ece452-b6c9-4153-8ed8-9073a1d19fe7" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoDeleteGroup"><strong>How to Delete Group</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6389b52e-5654-426c-81c7-56d68e8e125d">
<li local-id=3D"5a9dac9a-ceb2-4024-85cc-83416826557e">
<p local-id=3D"bae6c7fb-87c4-48f9-9116-2ff9f28dcd0e">Select the group you w=
