<li local-id=3D"405415e3-4832-4f85-94e4-a163f84fe607">
<p local-id=3D"3979f5fd-8d2f-4e45-b960-fa863f3b1611">If the group contains =
members, the system prompts:</p>
<p local-id=3D"c57af48e-ec1d-4a5c-8e8c-a6c262c23d7c">=E2=80=9CDeleting this=
 group will remove members=E2=80=99 access. Continue?=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78aa3dc2-f885-4399-92af-320c1f86fad4">
<p local-id=3D"60328f19-0123-42d9-9c2f-df8a1dfa423e">Confirm the deletion.<=
/p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"fb9c5ea8-00fc-4a28-ae9e-a0a92d26368e"><strong>Notes:</strong=
><br>
The group is deleted after confirmation, and all related permissions are re=
moved.</p>
