<h2 local-id=3D"194355af-1f39-4aad-a784-d85cf8e242d3" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-FXManagementSetting"><strong>FX Management Setting</strong></=
h2>
<p local-id=3D"478843ad-a86c-49cb-bd34-c4d361ac847f">The <strong>FX Managem=
ent</strong> module allows administrators to manage currencies, define exch=
ange rates, and control the system=E2=80=99s base currency.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"53c49646-26fb-4aa1-9d19-ec57848d72df" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoManageBasedCurrency"><strong>How to Manage Based Currenc=
y</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"c603ea98-1c42-454d-8032-6b0adb111d43">
<li local-id=3D"c383e0ad-7dbb-4bba-a397-be9410d2283a">
<p local-id=3D"37399638-f9e1-49b0-bbe6-8c7697dd8cf2">Navigate to the <stron=
g>FX Management</strong> section.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3140b6d3-eb67-4124-96cc-05eb2afef779">
<p local-id=3D"60e72d53-779b-4aa6-a01c-863b1e61494f">Review the current <st=
rong>Based Currency</strong> setting.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"009eb044-9dd9-4389-a8ff-577daf85aadc"><strong>Notes:</strong=
></p>
<ul local-id=3D"171867a3-b3ce-488d-a4ab-c0fc3ed8da41">
<li local-id=3D"ceb7704e-187a-4d89-90a0-5d90732a781b">
<p local-id=3D"befbb095-be2d-4bc8-9bb4-5e00ede5c42a">The based currency is =
currently fixed and <strong>cannot be changed</strong> once it selected thr=
ough the system.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ca93b75-efa7-4ec6-a338-a2e2ec858957">
<p local-id=3D"623d8185-89ef-4ad1-8804-161fba89a6b1">Any conversion rates a=
re always calculated relative to this based currency.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"30d46530-5286-4bfa-8dfa-4e8a07475ad7" id=3D"LabamuManufactu=
ringUserGuide-HowtoViewCurrencyList"><strong>How to View Currency List</str=
ong></h3>
