<p local-id=3D"4449c689-b5c3-4c51-be3c-ef929d3b311d">Navigate to <strong>Ad=
ministration =E2=86=92 FX Management =E2=86=92 Currency List</strong>.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"a1e90e28-0eff-4a8a-90bf-d7dcb9dcf77a">
<p local-id=3D"d07f2230-5858-49fd-850e-65c5d2ffa097">The system displays a =
list of all existing currencies.</p></li>
</ol>
