ringUserGuide-HowtoAddNewCurrency"><strong>How to Add New Currency</strong>=
</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"cdc6a482-a871-43df-b3ed-8397663c36bd">
<li local-id=3D"0d60fd7d-b485-4585-a501-9642b37de352">
<p local-id=3D"5abf10e6-d747-45ed-9984-6ba7e8910dc7">Click <strong>Add Curr=
ency</strong>.</p></li>
