<p local-id=3D"ec32dccc-e6a9-43bf-8190-514c0e2ba4b0">Choose Currency want t=
o add.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a397610-4a5c-4224-81bc-c250a079d7a2">
<p local-id=3D"07c76485-e290-4f10-b620-1a586a2ed5b8">Click <strong>Save</st=
