></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3307d0cc-af23-4d55-8338-8f53c3defe85">
<li local-id=3D"3218cda9-ee15-495d-9725-e8770754c667">
<p local-id=3D"bc55c47b-4793-45e7-8eaf-ea71226dec80">The new currency appea=
rs in the list immediately after saving.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d7023ca8-742c-4e94-90c5-5fabfd3fe3f6">
<p local-id=3D"5edde55d-5c85-41ea-b874-d959d96dd1de">If the currency code a=
lready exists, the system displays an error message:</p>
<p local-id=3D"77f70b0f-04ad-4bcc-b673-2736c6af6ccc">=E2=80=9CCurrency alre=
ady exists.=E2=80=9D</p></li>
</ul>
