ight=3D"167"></span>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e24a295f-91d3-4279-80ef-4e7265c20578">
<li local-id=3D"c7ee12f1-7e53-401a-a7fb-2fdcf5a518b3">
<p local-id=3D"c6462878-9df6-430d-ac79-ad904807ca11">Open the <strong>Excha=
nge Rate</strong> tab.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f6f2188-9873-4b13-9fe0-7b642ce37ade">
<p local-id=3D"7fe3120a-f506-4dd7-95f6-17bdc29aafe3">Click <strong>Add New =
Rate</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b0dc7363-e5fd-4864-9e23-10f125c213a5">
<p local-id=3D"2083aeff-fb8f-4648-a259-73c45458856d">Fill in the following =
fields:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"55887a22-84dd-4830-ab85-699e9a04d2ae">
<li local-id=3D"33b0cb2e-9000-4d3d-9441-15e953e16c66">
<p local-id=3D"fe92eb02-f258-4f8e-b515-dc19aef35446"><strong>From Currency<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 Select the source currency for the transaction (e.g., US=
D).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f456a97-198b-4626-b772-b334432a0c62">
<p local-id=3D"64d60005-6b54-468a-aedb-9659efc9ee0c"><strong>To Currency</s=
trong> =E2=80=93 Select the target currency for conversion (Default: Base C=
urrency).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6363e5bb-6836-4bce-82b8-95f96a1cd48b">
<p local-id=3D"246969f2-d4bb-4b10-aebd-541659fa56c4"><strong>Exchange Rate<=
/strong> =E2=80=93 Input the conversion rate between the selected currencie=
s (e.g., 15,500 IDR).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dcff6382-1114-4fcd-89e0-58771ea0ca6d">
<p local-id=3D"dcc65784-2cb2-4847-b4dc-72f0dba9016d"><strong>Effective Date=
</strong> =E2=80=93 Specify the date when the exchange rate becomes valid (=
e.g., 10 Oct 2025).</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ebb840c-7439-455d-a432-5379960d611a">
<p local-id=3D"818f5fb6-dae2-42fc-a4da-234c26354e95">Click <strong>Save</st=
rong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"bc915cf5-6cbc-47a3-bb30-824fa0d7cc6a"><strong>Notes:</strong=
></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d2a4b945-8302-4268-a516-43c41bf9b08f">
<li local-id=3D"ccc0003d-ed90-489d-8854-bf5626bbd9a7">
<p local-id=3D"fc55397a-a2d4-4805-bf55-08e701de14a2">The rate is saved and =
applied automatically from the specified effective date.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e3822f4-d2ee-4c61-a301-9935f0fa1605">
<p local-id=3D"35087338-6574-4db0-813d-e5419a32f4b9">If the effective date =
is not entered, the system displays an error message</p></li>
</ul>
